  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-link\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-link/`\n**NOTE:** No index.ts — may be incomplete/from PR 175 rescue.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Existence Check** — Complete implementation? Document gaps.\n2. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Color, hover color, visited, underline. Dark mode.\n3. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Anchor semantics. External link indicator. New window warning.\n4. **Functionality** — href, target, rel. External link detection. Download attribute. Disabled state.\n5. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n6. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. Underline variants. Color states. Focus-ring.\n7. **CEM Accuracy** — Must be documented if shipping.\n8. **Tests** — Navigation. External link. Disabled. ARIA.\n9. **Storybook** — Internal/external. Disabled. Variants.\n10. **Drupal Compatibility** — Twig link. Menu items.\n\n### Deliverable\nIf incomplete: document gaps. If complete: full audit. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH.",
